I'll work through the formal proof of the theorem `lengthOfLIS_spec_satisfied` which states that for any list of integers `nums`, the length of the longest increasing subsequence (LIS) computed by the `lengthOfLIS` function satisfies the properties defined in `lengthOfLIS_postcond`.

